Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.96,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... it’s hot... so hot!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.18,0:00:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it like this every single day?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.03,0:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This heat just keeps coming\Nwhether we want it or not... {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.41,0:00:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But complaining about the heat \Nwon’t change anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.16,0:00:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, yeah, but that’s kind of killing the mood. {blunt; to the point; direct; outspoken; frank}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.90,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t there some way to cool down? Like something\Nthat sends chills all the way down your spine.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.02,0:00:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.16,0:00:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when you eat one of Madoka’s cookies, \Nsomething that intense.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.01,0:00:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.14,0:00:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Madoka! I-I was joking! \NA joke! Come on, laugh! Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.37,0:01:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.58,0:01:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that’s not a “haha, funny” face at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.05,0:01:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.94,0:01:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.32,0:01:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, Madoka! It was my fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.79,0:01:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.35,0:01:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. The usual, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.08,0:01:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.76,0:01:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Madoka, what are you trying to do here?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.69,0:01:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.36,0:01:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, w-why are\Nyou putting the coffee there...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.48,0:01:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Pastel...?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.06,0:01:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t scream like that, \Nyou’re bothering the other customers.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.81,0:01:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going home...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.56,0:01:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See you...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.80,0:01:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, so clamorous.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the disturbance. {dont ask me Ive no clue what's this supposed to mean}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.74,0:02:03.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.96,0:02:06.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,What on Earth is Madoka, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:09.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,
